reviews.title: Star Trek Computer Soundboard
reviews.comment: What can I say about this app?!... {:-D TOTALLY FLAWLESS!!! B-) Way Cool!!! Awsum Job!!! I\'ll be looking for more of your work! Thank you, I\'m having lots a fun with these sounds with my \"LCARS UI\" App. My Tekkie friend\'s all want it.
reviews.author: David Peterson

reviews.title: Excellent!
reviews.comment: Excellent collection. (and huge)  Good quality sounds, minimal background noise.  Missing the red alert klaxon though.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great app!
reviews.comment: Love this app! It must contain every saying from the on board computer not to mention plenty of computer chirps and beeps. This person obviously spent a lot of time gathering all of these sounds for this app. Previous updates have included more sounds. Looking forward to the next update!
reviews.author: Rodney Mohawk

reviews.title: Best for notifications
reviews.comment: A few have a sudden cut off that you can hear mostly through your blue tooth a little bit through your speaker but most are pretty darn good. They do have a Dolby quality to them. I suspect the cut off is so that the entire track from the movie is not heard. Still I like I keep :-)
reviews.author: Thomas Perkins
